# ğŸ½ï¸ QR Menu â€“ Restaurant Management System

A **QR-based Restaurant Menu & Management System** built using **FastAPI (Backend)** and **React + Vite (Frontend)**.
The system supports **role-based authentication**, **multi-restaurant management**, and **dynamic menus with pricing sizes**.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

### ğŸ‘‘ Admin

* Login (no registration)
* Create restaurants
* Create global menu categories
* Control platform data

### ğŸ½ï¸ Restaurant

* Login using credentials created by Admin
* Manage own products only
* Add products with **multiple sizes & prices**
* Upload product images
* Toggle product availability

### ğŸ‘¥ Customer (Public)

* No login required
* View restaurant menu via QR code
* Browse categories & products

---

## ğŸ—ï¸ Tech Stack

### Backend

* **FastAPI**
* **PostgreSQL**
* **SQLAlchemy**
* **Alembic (Migrations)**
* **JWT Authentication**
* **Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)**

### Frontend

* **React**
* **Vite**
* **Tailwind CSS**
* **Axios**
* **Zustand (State Management)**

