## ğŸ§¾ Example API Endpoints

### Create Restaurant (Admin)

```
POST /api/v1/restaurants/
```

### Restaurant Login

```
POST /auth/login
```

### Create Product (Restaurant)

```
POST /api/v1/restaurants/{restaurant_id}/products/
```

### Public Menu

```
GET /api/v1/restaurants/{restaurant_id}/products/
```

---

## ğŸ“± QR Menu Concept

Each restaurant gets a **QR code** pointing to:

```
/restaurants/{restaurant_id}/menu
```

Customers scan QR â†’ view live menu â†’ no app install.

